	This lovely fair trade dark wooden ornament is a plain carving of a praying angel with no facial features.&nbsp; This angel is hand made so the sizes do vary slightly but the approximate height is 10cm.&nbsp; Angels are messengers from the higher realm, ready to provide us with emotional reassurances and spiritual guidance.&nbsp; Carved angels help us to connect with our own guardian angels who guard and protect us in all that we ask.&nbsp; This carved angel is a very popular item that would look good in any home and makes an ideal gift for a loved one.</p>
